snippet.title: Glorious Tournius - Gameplay Trailer 2020 - Active Ragdoll Physics
snippet.description:
This is gameplay from the demo level of Glorius Tournius. Demo to be released on itch.io on Saturday 20th June.

4 player battles with a variety of weapons and explosions with active ragdoll physics.
